data.text: We're excited to share with you our Annual Report for 2022 and reflect on our successes and impacts from the last year. Our report links the activities of IGHI and its Centres of Excellence with our themes, which we continue to focus on in 2023: Prevention and early detection Healthcare delivery Health equity Safety and quality Emerging global challenges Take a look at our digital report to see how we have been tackling the healthcare challenges of the present and the future: https://lnkd.in/esXb4yNs
